quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  19,73,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá ń ké àwọn āyah Wa tó yanjú fún wọn, àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ yóò sọ fún àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo pé: “Èwo nínú ìjọ méjèèjì (àwa tàbí ẹ̀yin) ló lóore jùlọ ní ibùgbé, ló sì dára jùlọ ní ìjókòó (afẹ́)?”"
  19,74,"Àti pé mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn ìran tí A ti parẹ́ ṣíwájú wọn, tí wọ́n dára jù wọ́n lọ ní ọrọ̀ (ayé) àti ní ìrísí!"
  19,75,"Sọ pé: “Ẹni tí ó bá wà nínú ìṣìnà, Àjọkẹ́-ayé yó sì fẹ (ìṣìnà) lójú fún un tààrà, títí di ìgbà tí wọn máa rí ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fún wọn, yálà ìyà tàbí Àkókò náà. Nígbà náà, wọn yóò mọ ẹni tí ó burú jùlọ ní ipò, tí ó sì lẹ jùlọ ní ọmọ ogun."
  20,55,"Láti ara erùpẹ̀ ni A ti da yín. Inú rẹ̀ sì ni A óò da yín padà sí. Láti inú rẹ̀ sì ni A óò ti mu yín jáde padà nígbà mìíràn.”"
  20,56,"Dájúdájú A ti fi àwọn àmì Wa hàn án, gbogbo rẹ̀. Àmọ́ ó pè é ní irọ́. Ó sì kọ̀ jálẹ̀."
  20,57,"Ó wí pé: “Ṣé o wá bá wa nítorí kí o lè mú wa jáde kúrò lórí ilẹ̀ wa pẹ̀lú idán rẹ ni, Mūsā?"
  21,31,"A sì fi àwọn àpáta tó dúró gbagidi sínú ilẹ̀ kí ó má fi lè mì mọ́ wọn lẹ́sẹ̀. A sì fi àwọn ọ̀nà fífẹ̀ sáààrin àwọn àpáta nítorí kí wọ́n lè rí ọ̀nà tọ̀."
  21,32,"A tún ṣe sánmọ̀ ní àjà tí wọ́n ń ṣọ́ (níbi jíjábọ́). Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ wọ́n ń gbúnrí kúrò níbi àwọn àmì rẹ̀."
  21,33,"Òun ni Ẹni tí Ó dá òru àti ọ̀sán pẹ̀lú òòrùn àti òṣùpá. Ìkọ̀ọ̀kan (òòrùn àti òṣùpá) wà ní òpópónà roboto tó ń tọ̀."
  22,7,"Àti pé dájúdájú Àkókò náà ń bọ̀. Kò sí iyèméjì nínú rẹ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu yóò gbé àwọn tó ń bẹ nínú sàréè dìde."
  22,8,"Ó ń bẹ nínú àwọn ènìyàn ẹni tó ń jiyàn nípa (ẹ̀sìn) Allāhu láì ní ìmọ̀ (al-Ƙur’ān) àti ìmọ̀nà (sunnah Ànábì) àti tírà (onímọ̀-ẹ̀sìn) tó ń tan ìmọ́lẹ̀ (sí ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀sìn)."
  22,9,"Ó ń ṣègbéraga (sí òdodo, ó ń gbúnrí kúrò níbi òdodo) nítorí kí ó lè kó ìṣìnà bá àwọn ènìyàn lójú ọ̀nà (ẹ̀sìn) Allāhu. Àbùkù ń bẹ fún un nílé ayé. Ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde, A sì máa fún un ní ìyà Iná jónijóni tọ́ wò."